dc_description_s: This point shapefile contains locations of lighthouses on the California coast. This layer was created using web-based research on coastal lighthouse locations. Point locations were created by using aerial photography. Each lighthouse was attributed with its operation status.This coverage depicts lighthouses on the California coast.
